k <- matrix(k, nrow=10, byrow=T)

np <- nrow(k)
nq <- ncol(k)

data <- list("np","nq","k") # to be passed on to JAGS
myinits <- list(
  list(q = runif(nq), p = runif(np)))

# parameters to be monitored:   
parameters <- c("p", "q")

2.2 Model & MCMC

model_text <- "
# Twenty Questions
model{
  # Correctness Of Each Answer Is Bernoulli Trial
  for (i in 1:np){
    for (j in 1:nq){
      k[i,j] ~ dbern(theta[i,j])
    }
  }
  
  # Probability Correct Is Product Of Question By Person Rates
  for (i in 1:np){
    for (j in 1:nq){
      theta[i,j] <- p[i]*q[j]
    }
  }
  
  # Priors For People and Questions
  for (i in 1:np){
    p[i] ~ dbeta(1,1)
  }
  for (j in 1:nq){
    q[j] ~ dbeta(1,1)
  }
}
"

samples1 <- jags(data, inits=myinits, parameters,
                 model.file = textConnection(model_text), 
                 n.chains=1, n.iter=2000, 
         n.burnin=1, n.thin=1, DIC=T)

  pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("NA"), 
               names_to = "NA_array", values_to = "Value") %>% 
  group_by(NA_array) %>% 
  summarise(Mean = mean(Value),
            SD = sd(Value)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%  
  ggplot(aes(x = NA_array, y = Mean)) +

  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=ifelse(Mean-SD<0,0,Mean-SD), 
                    ymax=ifelse(Mean+SD>1,1,Mean+SD)), width=.2, color = "darkred") +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 1, by = 0.2)) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.minor = element_blank())
